{"tid":208391,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩納哥3:2多蒙特，巴塞1:1祖雲，摩納哥祖雲晉級四強","createTime":"2017-04-19T13:24:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T05:11:43.000Z","uid":51951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0b01a7141858938af90b5f375e81b84ee7a5e67a","tid":208391,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:24:34.000Z","msg":"摩納哥再以同樣比數擊敗多蒙特，兩回合6:4晉級<br />\n<br />\n巴塞美斯1:0先，之後祖雲戴巴拿1:1追和，祖雲兩回合4:1晉級<br />\n<br />\n4強已定，皇馬面對馬體祖雲摩納哥，形勢大好，幾乎肯定可以衛冕歐聯<br />\n<br />\n今天不結衣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5140Mw9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5140Mw9.png&h=87f88e88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5w65T9B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5w65T9B.png&h=3b2d0d52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6v6D1z6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6v6D1z6.png&h=5dbd13a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XU0237s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXU0237s.png&h=a7b02b85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83t0C7g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83t0C7g.png&h=e0ca2e28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnvP654.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnnvP654.png&h=287563d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n摩納哥挑戰唔到皇馬，馬體歐聯無論兩回合同一場過，對皇馬都輸硬，皇馬唯一出局機會係四強對祖雲，決賽都唔得，祖雲決賽往積近乎必敗，亞軍王，如果四強皇馬對馬摩，決賽對祖，咁皇馬肯定衛冕，如果祖雲四強攔不住皇馬，咁皇馬就天下無敵了。"},{"pid":"6999ded6671c1080ea85f837d04325b9c96dde89","tid":208391,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"法卡奧，樂天，香川，奧巴入波，萊斯助攻"},{"pid":"20df34b593378b7a0af64659eae6a0b5e08e324b","tid":208391,"uid":3